    "synopsis": "Kal Jerico returns to Hive Primus chasing the richest bounty of his career: Desolation Zoon, a Redemptionist preacher tearing through the Underhive in a mining hauler loaded with stolen Guilder guns. The reward draws every serious Venator in the hive, turning the pursuit into a running gang-war chase with Kal at its smirking center. Built for readers meeting Kal fresh, it plays as modern Necromunda action-comedy, all banter, collapsing plans, rival hunters and bad decisions made at full hive speed.",
